'''额上沟'''（{{lang-en|Superior frontal sulcus}}），是[[大脑|大脑]][[额叶|额叶]]的主要[[脑沟|脑沟]]之一，隔开了[[额上回|额上回]]与[[额中回|额中回]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Superior Frontal Sulcus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/superior-frontal-sulcus|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Superior frontal sulcus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/superior-frontal-sulcus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-09|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=额上沟|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/2735|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=IMAIOS|language=cn}}</ref>

== 功能 ==
